{"tid":1784370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣Youtuber波特王Potter King同支那玻璃心割蓆","createTime":"2019-12-15T15:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T16:14:40.000Z","uid":162061,"like":86,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"0609798d793e3e8299a22e38e13f9259f58013f4","tid":1784370,"uid":162061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T15:24:11.000Z","msg":"昨天才剛解鎖人生成就，今天就有突發狀況。<br />\n.<br />\n以下是我們中國新媒體合作方的訊息，之前其實就有跟他們說過不要干涉我們的創作內容了。<br />\n.<br />\n而今天他們不只干涉還過頭了<br />\n他們的重點放在「總統」兩個字都不能出現，看到這裡我跟Mars他們討論後完全沒辦法接受，真的太扯了。<br />\n.<br />\n然後我微博大概一百多萬人<br />\n帳號都是我們自己經營的，直接被他們改密碼端走，現在登入不進去了。<br />\n.<br />\n如果要我們不能稱呼自己國家的元首為「總統」那這筆錢我們不賺也罷....<br />\n.<br />\n這每個月損失雖然不小，但我們真的跪不下去。<br />\n<br />\n#很多台灣人覺得民主很正常<br />\n#實際上民主真他媽可貴<br />\nSource: 佢facebook<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/15/232308_7abe6e4c60def0a32fa32c8fa44151f1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F15%2F232308_7abe6e4c60def0a32fa32c8fa44151f1.png&h=ebf94c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/15/232310_f30713d7b074f1c0862ca5fce9b9e594.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F15%2F232310_f30713d7b074f1c0862ca5fce9b9e594.png&h=f0013ae2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/15/232312_70a8ca526c4fc6ec9ba94d9c77a77a30.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F15%2F232312_70a8ca526c4fc6ec9ba94d9c77a77a30.png&h=e5e22495&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/15/232314_88167e598d5b260a9bbc15f8fd812948.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F15%2F232314_88167e598d5b260a9bbc15f8fd812948.png&h=c34d84bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/15/232315_6a13